                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040111-71-off420 t18040111-71-cd421"></join>, a tub, value 6 d. and a peck of oysters, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18040111-71-victim752" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Noble
                  <interp inst="t18040111-71-victim752" type="surname" value="Noble"></interp>
